title: Labour: Hilary Benn says party could support RAF air strikes in Syria
text: Labour has indicated it could support the extension of RAF airstrikes against the Islamic State terror group ( Isis ) into Syria without the backing of a United Nations Security Council resolution . The party 's annual conference last month
